  "content": "<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How does Atlantic Canada business funding work?</h2>\n              <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  Atlantic Canada operates a unique business funding ecosystem with approximately $850 million\n                  available annually through federal and provincial programs. The Atlantic Canada Opportunities\n                  Agency (ACOA) serves as the primary federal agency, providing substantial funding that\n                  complements each province's own programs.\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  The region's economic development priorities focus on ocean technology, clean energy,\n                  digital innovation, and diversifying traditional industries like fishing and forestry.\n                  Atlantic Canada's smaller population means less competition for funding compared to\n                  major urban centers, making it one of the more accessible funding environments in Canada.\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"bg-indigo-50 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 p-4 my-6\">\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                    <strong>Key Insight:</strong> ACOA funding is often the best starting point for\n                    Atlantic businesses. The agency offers both repayable and non-repayable contributions,\n                    with interest-free loans being particularly attractive for eligible projects.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4\">Atlantic Canada Opportunities Agency (ACOA)</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n                ACOA is the federal regional development agency serving Atlantic Canada with comprehensive\n                business development programs and funding opportunities.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12\">\n                {/* ACOA Business Development Program */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">ACOA Business Development Program</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $500K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Growth & Innovation</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      ACOA's flagship program provides interest-free repayable contributions\n                      and non-repayable grants for business expansion, modernization, and\n                      competitiveness enhancement.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Business expansion and modernization</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Innovation and technology adoption</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Export market development</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* ACOA Innovation Program */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Regional Economic Growth through Innovation</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $1M</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>R&D Focus</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      REGI provides funding for innovative projects that drive regional economic\n                      growth, including R&D, technology commercialization, and ecosystem development.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>R&D project funding</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Commercialization support</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Technology partnerships</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Atlantic Immigration Pilot */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Atlantic Growth Strategy</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Variable</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Workforce</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Multi-faceted federal initiative supporting Atlantic business growth\n                      through workforce development, immigration, and strategic investment.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Skilled workforce attraction</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>International market access</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Strategic investments</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Women Entrepreneurship Fund */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Women Entrepreneurship Strategy</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $100K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Women-Led</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Targeted funding for Atlantic women entrepreneurs and women-led businesses\n                      seeking to start, grow, or expand operations.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Women-owned business support</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Scale-up funding</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Ecosystem development</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12\">What provincial programs are available in each Atlantic province?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\">\n                {/* Nova Scotia */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Nova Scotia Business Programs</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>$5K - $500K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Nova Scotia offers multiple programs through Invest Nova Scotia, including\n                      the Small Business Development Program and sector-specific incentives.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Small Business Development Program</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Payroll Rebate for Technology</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Digital Innovation Programs</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* New Brunswick */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">New Brunswick Business Programs</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>$10K - $200K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      New Brunswick Innovation Foundation and Opportunities New Brunswick\n                      provide funding for technology development and business growth.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>NB Innovation Foundation grants</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Opportunities NB programs</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Bilingual workforce incentives</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* PEI */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Prince Edward Island Programs</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>$10K - $150K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Innovation PEI offers development funding, while the PEI Development Fund\n                      supports job creation and rural business development.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Innovation PEI grants</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Rural economic development</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Tourism and agriculture focus</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Newfoundland */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Newfoundland & Labrador Programs</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>$25K - $300K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Newfoundland offers programs through the Department of Industry, Energy\n                      and Technology, with special focus on ocean and energy sectors.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Business investment grants</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Ocean technology funding</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Remote community support</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Who is Eligible for Atlantic Canada Business Grants?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                Atlantic Canada grants are available to for-profit enterprises with operations in one\n                of the four Atlantic provinces. ACOA programs serve all four provinces, while\n                provincial programs have province-specific requirements.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Generally Eligible\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Incorporated in an Atlantic province</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>SMEs with significant Atlantic operations</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Projects creating regional economic impact</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Good standing with tax authorities</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Generally Ineligible\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses without Atlantic operations</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Projects completed before approval</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses in tax arrears</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Real estate speculation</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Much Grant Funding Can Atlantic Businesses Get?</h2>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-indigo-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Program</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Typical Range</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Cost Share</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">ACOA BDP</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$50K - $500K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">50%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">ACOA REGI</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$100K - $1M</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">50-70%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Provincial Programs</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$10K - $300K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Variable</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Atlantic businesses can often stack ACOA federal funding\n                  with provincial programs, maximizing total support. Coordinate applications to\n                  avoid conflicts and ensure both applications reference each other.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How to Apply for Atlantic Canada Grants - Step by Step</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-6\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">1</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Contact ACOA Regional Office</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      ACOA encourages early contact. Reach out to your provincial office\n                      to discuss your project and identify suitable programs.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">2</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Prepare Application Package</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Complete application forms with business plan, project description,\n                      budget, and financial statements. ACOA provides templates.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">3</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Submit & Due Diligence</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      ACOA conducts thorough assessment including site visits for larger\n                      projects. Provincial programs may have shorter review cycles.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">4</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Contribution Agreement</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Upon approval, sign agreement outlining terms, milestones, and\n                      reporting requirements. ACOA uses milestone-based payments.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Required Documents for Atlantic Canada Grant Applications</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Business Documents\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Corporate registration</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>2-3 years of financial statements</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Current year financials</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Ownership documentation</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Project Documents\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Detailed project plan</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Budget with vendor quotes</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Cash flow projections</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Market analysis</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Long Does Atlantic Canada Grant Approval Take?</h2>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-indigo-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Program Type</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Review Timeline</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">ACOA BDP (smaller projects)</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">30-60 days</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">ACOA BDP (larger projects)</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">60-120 days</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Provincial Programs</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">30-90 days</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Common Mistakes to Avoid with Atlantic Canada Grant Applications</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">1</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Not Contacting ACOA First</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          ACOA encourages pre-application discussions. Skipping this step\n                          means missing valuable guidance and potentially applying to the\n                          wrong program.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">2</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Weak Regional Impact Documentation</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Atlantic programs prioritize regional economic impact. Applications\n                          must clearly demonstrate job creation, export potential, and\n                          community benefits.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">3</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Ignoring Provincial Programs</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Many applicants focus only on ACOA. Provincial programs can\n                          stack with federal funding and often have faster approval times.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Which industries get the most Atlantic Canada funding?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Ocean Technology</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Aquaculture, marine research, offshore energy</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Clean Energy</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Wind, tidal, hydrogen, sustainability</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Digital Economy</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Software, gaming, fintech, AI</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Aerospace & Defence</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Aircraft maintenance, defense tech</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Fishing & Seafood</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Processing, export, sustainability</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Tourism</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Eco-tourism, cultural tourism</p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Major City Business Programs</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Halifax, Nova Scotia</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Halifax Partnership economic programs</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Volta – Tech accelerator</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Ocean tech hub programs</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">St. John's, Newfoundland</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                   